# Skills and Expertise

Your skills define what you can do beyond raw physical and mental capability. While attributes measure your inherent potential, skills measure your learned expertise—the training, practice, and experience that let you apply your natural talents effectively.

Every action in Autumn Phoenix RPG combines an attribute with a skill. Your attribute provides the foundation; your skill provides the refinement. A character with high Might but low Combat skill can throw a strong punch but lacks the training to use it effectively. A character with modest Might but high Combat skill compensates through technique and expertise.

